<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q21_v7" title="Q21_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>¿Cuál de los siguientes números es igual a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac></m:math>?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Se tiene <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, y <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> porque, por ejemplo, <m:math><m:msup><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, la expresión dada es igual a <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión vale <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, y <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Se obtiene <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Además, <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, que es distinto de <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la expresión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión del enunciado es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Usar la propiedad de radicales</strong></p>
            <p>Como ambos radicales son raíces cuadradas y el denominador es positivo, se puede escribir:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar la fracción interior</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:msqrt><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa B es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, que coincide exactamente con el resultado obtenido.</p>
            <p>Las demás no coinciden:</p>
            <p>Opción A: <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Opción C: <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math></p>
            <p>Opción D: <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El número igual a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:msqrt><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mfrac></m:math> es <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>. Por lo tanto, la respuesta correcta es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>